      <li>Characterization: SCXRD, PXRD, PDF, SAXS; IR, Raman, luminescence spectroscopy; multinuclear NMR (¹H, ¹³C, ³¹P, ¹¹⁹Sn, ¹⁸³W); SEM, AFM, X-ray tomography, etc.
</li>
